title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 2 categories of Worker Type on the x axis representing 5 groups: 2013, 2014, 2015, 2016, and 2017.
Averaging the 5 groups, the highest category is found for Worker Type Regular workers with a mean value of 21620.0.
The minimum category is found at Temporary workers with a mean value of 3600.0.

In case of Regular workers, 2013 shows more dominance than any other Worker Type and it has the lowest value in Temporary workers. On the other hand, group 2017 is highest in case of Regular workers and has minimum impact for Worker Type Temporary workers.
